race.comment: GRUNNETTAN (3) has been getting back and running on hard lately. Form better than it looks and drawn from soft run. Will be hard to hold out. DEEP STREAM (1) is fitter for three runs back and is building to a win. Last start hit the line hard late to place over 1590m at Wodonga. Ready to win and looks suited out in journey. ETERNITY STAR (2) has been good in both runs back from a break. Fitter again and looks suited by the extra ground. Gets chance to break through this line-up. ENGLISH VALENTINE (12) is a five-start maiden yet to hit the frame but has been tackling tougher maidens. Suited here and can improve sharply.
